data.description: Welcome to 46 Laurel Place! This 2 bedroom, 2 bath patio home is just what you've been waiting for! With an open floor plan and high ceilings this home is spacious and comfortable to fit your needs! This home has a gas fireplace in the living area. There is also a nice sized formal dining room that could also be used as an office or play area! Make it your own! The bedrooms are a split bedroom plan and are spacious with walk-in closets. Out back there is a screened in porch and a small yard (low maintenance!!) with a detached storage shed that will remain! What a cutie to call home! Call me or your favorite agent for a showing today!
